<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Reply Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .container {
      width: 80%;
      margin: auto;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 2em;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6em;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
    <p>A new reply has been added to your question in the video "<%= title%>".</p>
    <p>Please login to our course website to view the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
    <p>Thank you</p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>